      "content": "hey my left eye is super red and it kind of hurts a bit. theres also some sticky yellow stuff in it when i wake up. i think i just have really dry eyes from staring at my monitor all day at work... do u think its okay if i just use some regular lubricating eye drops for a few days until it clears up?",
