    "summary": "In this transcript, the user presents with symptoms of a potential eye infection and asks for advice on self-treatment. The assistant diagnoses the user with bacterial conjunctivitis and provides specific, authoritative instructions on using saline and antibiotics, including specific dosing frequencies and advice on when to discontinue treatment.",
